hadiths[224]{hadithnumber,text}:
5155,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do nematen aisi hain, jinkey barey mein bahut se log khasaray mein hain : sehat aur faraaghat.'' Bukhari."
5156,"Hazrat Mustaurid bin Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah ki qism ! aakhirat ke muqabley mein duniya ki misal bas aisey hi hai jaisey tum mein se koi apni ungli samandar mein duboey , phir wo dekhey ke wo (ungli pani ki) kitni miqdaar ke sath lot'ti hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5157,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bakri ke eik chhotey kanon waley murdar bachchey ke paas se guzrey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se kon usey eik dirham mein lena pasand kerega?'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : ham to usey kisi maamuli chiz ke badley mein lena bhi pasand nahin kartey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! Allah ke nazdik duniya us se bhi ziyada haqeer hai jitna ye ( bakri ka murda bachcha) tumharey nazdik haqeer hai.'' rawahu Muslim.
5158,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''duniya momin ke liye qaid khana jabkey kafir ke liye jannat hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5159,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah kisi momin ki koi neki zaya nahin karta , usko us ( neki (ke badley mein duniya mein ata kya jata hai aur uskey badley mein usey aakhirat mein jaza di jaeygi, aur kafir ko uski duniya mein Allah ke liye ki gaee nekiyon ke badley mein khilaya jata hai, yahan tak ke jab wo aakhirat ko pahunchega to uski koi neki nahin hogi jiski usey jaza di jaey. rawahu Muslim."
5160,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam ko shehwaat ke sath dhanp diya gaya hai aur jannat ko nagawar chizon se dhanp diya gaya hai.'' Bukhari, Muslim. albatta sahih Muslim mein) حجبت (ke badley ( hiffat (ke alfaz hain. muttafaq aleh."
5161,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''deenar w dirham aur do-shaaley ka (parastaar ( banda halak hua , agar usey diya jaey to khush aur agar na diya jaey to naraz hota hai, wo halak hua aur zaleel hua , jab usey kaanta chubhey to wo nikala na jaey, khush haali ho us shakhs ke liye jo Allah ki raah mein apney ghodey ki lagaam thaamey huey hai, uskey baal paraganda aur paaon gard-aalood hain, agar wo pehrey par maamoor hai to wo pehrey par data hua hai aur agar lashkar ke aakhiri dastey mein hai to wo wahan bhi data hua hai, agar wo ( mahfil mein shirkat ke liye ( ijazat talab karey to usey ijazat na di jaey aur agar wo sifarish karey to sifarish qubul na ki jaey.'' Bukhari ."
5162,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey apney baad tumharey mutalliq jis chiz ka andesha hai wo ye hai ke tum par duniya ki ronaq aur uski zeenat ka darwaza khol diya jaeyga.'' eik aadmi ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya khair , burai ko sath layegi? aap khamosh rahey yahan tak ke ham ne guman kya ke aap par wahi utaari ja rahi hai, raawi bayan kartey hain, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney (chehrey mubarak) se paseena saaf kya, aur farmaya : ''wo saail kahan hai?'' goya aapney uski tareef ki, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khair, shar ko sath nahin layegi, be-shak mausam Rabeea jo chaara ugata hai, us se wo baaz chaara janwer ko maar daalta hai, aphaaraa kar deta hai ya halakat ke qarib kar deta hai, albatta sabz (hara) ghaas khaney wala janwer khata hai yahan tak ke uskey kokh nikal aatey hain, wo Suraj ki taraf rukh karkey jugaali karta hai, gobar karta hai aur peshab karta hai, aur wo dobara ( charney ( chala jata hai aur dobara ( sabz (hara) ghaas ( khata hai, ye maal sarsabz w shadab , sheereen hai jisney usey apni zarurat ke mutabiq liya aur usey uskey haq ke mutabiq kharch kya to wo behtareen madadgar hai, aur jisney usey apni zarurat ke baghair hasil kya to wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jo khata hai lekin sair nahin hota aur wo ( maal ( roze-qiyamat uskey khilaf gawahi dega .'' muttafaq aleh."
5163,"Hazrat Amr bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! main tumharey mutalliq faqr se nahin darta lekin mujhey tumharey mutalliq is baat ka andesha hai ke duniya tum par faraakh kar di jaeygi jaisey tum se pehley logon par faraakh ki gaee thi, phir tum uskey mutalliq wesay hi raghbat rakhogey jaisey unhoney uskey mutalliq raghbat rakhi, aur wo tumhen halak kar degi jaisey usney unhen halak kar diya.'' muttafaq aleh."
5164,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dua farmaai : ''aey Allah ! aal Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sirf itna rizq ata farma ke unke jism w jaan ka rishta barqarar reh sakey .'' muttafaq aleh. eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''guzaarey key laaiq rozi ata farma (
5165,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us shakhs ne falah pai jisney (apney rab ki) itaat kar li aur usey b-qadr zarurat rizq ata kya gaya aur Allah ne jo usey ata kya is par usney qanaa-at ikhtiyar ki .'' rawahu Muslim ."
5166,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' banda kehta hai, mera maal , mera maal , halanke uska maal faqat teen Suraton mein hai jo usney kha kar khatam kar diya, ya pehan kar boseedah kar diya ya ( Allah ki raah mein) de-kar zakhira kar liya , aur jo unke ilawa hai wo to usey logon ke liye chhod kar janey wala hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5167,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maiyat ke sath teen chizen jati hain, un mein se do wapis aa jati hain aur eik uskey sath baqi rehti hai. uskey ghar waley, uska maal aur uskey aamaal uskey sath jatey hain, uskey ghar waley aur uska maal wapis aa jatey hain, aur uskey aamaal ( uskey sath ( baqi reh jatey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
5168,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se kon hai jisey apney warison ka maal apney maal se ziyada pasand hai? '' Sahaba ne arz kya : ham mein se her eik ko apna maal apney warison ke maal se ziyada pasand hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak uska maal to wo hai jo usney aagey bheja jabkey wo maal jo usney peechey chhoda wo uskey warison ka hai.'' Bukhari ."
5169,"Hazrat Mutrif apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aap (us waqt ( Sura takasur ki tilawat farma rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ibne-Adam kehta hai : mera maal , mera maal , aey ibne-Adam ! halanke tera maal to sirf wo hai jo to ne khaya aur khatam kar diya, ya pehan liya aur boseedah kar diya ya sadqa karkey ( aakhirat ke liye ( aagey bhej diya .'' rawahu Muslim ."
5170,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maal daari, maal aur saazo-saman ki kasrat se hasil nahin hoti, balke maaldaari to nafs ki maaldaari (yani qanaa'at) hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5171,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kon hai jo mujh se ye kalmaat seekhey aur un par amal karey ya kisi aisey shakhs ko sikhaey jo un par amal karey ?'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! main , chunanche aapney mera haath pakad aur paanch chizen shumar kin , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' muhaarim ( Allah ki haram karda chizon ( se bach jaao , is tarah tum sab logon se ziyada ibadat guzar bin jaaogey, Allah ne jo tumhari qismat mein likh diya hai is par razi ho jaao is tarah tum sab logon se ziyada ghani bin jaaogey, apney padosi se achcha suluk karogey to momin bin jaaogey, logon ke liye wohi chiz pasand karo jo tum apni zaat ke liye pasand kartey ho, to musalman bin jaeyga, ziyada mat hansa karo kyonkey ziyada hansna dil ko murda kar deta hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi ."
5172,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah farmata hai : insan! meri ibadat ke liye farigh ho ja, mein terey dil ko maal daari (qanaa'at) se bhar dunga, teri mohtaji khatam kar dunga aur agar to ( aisey ( nahin kerega to main tumhen kamon mein masroof kar dunga aur teri mohtaji khatam nahin karunga.'' rawahu Ahmed w ibne-Maja ."
5173,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik aadmi ki ibadat aur is mein bharpur inhimaak ka zikr kya gaya aur doosrey aadmi ka taqwa w ehtiyat baratney ka zikr kya gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' taqwa ke sath (us ibadat w ijtihaad ka ( muwaazna na karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5174,"Hazrat Amr bin Memun Awdi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko nasihat kartey huey farmaya : '' paanch chizon ko paanch chizon se pehley ghanimat samjho , apni jawani ko apney budhapey se pehley , apni sehat ko apney marz se pehley , apney maal daar honey ko apni mohtaji se pehley , apni faraaghat ko apni masroofiyat se pehley aur apni zindagi ko apni maut se pehley .'' Imam Tirmizi ne isey mursal riwayat kya hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
5175,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi had se tajawuz kar deney wali tawangari ka intizar karta hai, ya ( ibadat w itaat sey) bhala deney wali mohtaji ka intizar karta hai, ya kharab kar deney waley marz ka, ya be-hooda goi karaney waley budhapey ka, ya achcha aa janey wali maut ka, ya dajjaal ka, dajjaal to poshida fitna hai jiska intizar hai, ya qiyamat ka aur qiyamat badi aafat aur nagawar chiz hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai."
5176,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo! duniya aur jo kuch is mein hai sab maloon hain, haan ! albatta Allah ka zikr, Allah ke pasandida aamaal aur aalim w Mutallim is se mustashna hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
5177,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar duniya (ki ahmiyat) Allah ke nazdik machar ke par ke barabar bhi hoti to wo kisi kafir ko is mein se pani ka ghoont bhi na pilata.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
5178,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jaageerein mat banaao warna tum duniya mein munhamik ho jaaogey .'' ( rawahu Tirmizi w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5179,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney duniya ko pasand kya, usney aakhirat ka nuqsan kya aur jisney aakhirat ko pasand kya to usney duniya ko nuqsan pahunchaya , tum baqi rehney wali chiz ko fana honey wali chiz par tarjeeh do .'' ( rawahu Ahmed w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5180,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dirham w Dinar ka banda maloon hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5181,"Hazrat Kab bin Malik apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do bhookey bhediye, jinhen bakriyon ke rewad mein chhoda jaey to wo unke liye itna nuqsan deh nahin jitni aadmi ke maal w jah ki hirs uskey Deen ke liye nuqsan deh hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Darmi."
5182,"Hazrat Khabbab (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' momin jo bhi kharch karta hai to is par usey ajr milta hai lekin usney jo kharch is mitti par zarurat se zyada kya is par usey ajr nahin milta .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5183,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sara kharcha Allah ki raah mein siwaye taameerat ke , us (par kharch kerney) mein koi khair nahin.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5184,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik roz bahar tashrif laye aur ham aap ke sath they, aapney eik ooncha sa qubba dekha to farmaya : ''ye kya hai? '' aap ke Sahaba ne arz kya, ye eik Ansari shakhs ka hai, aap khamosh ho gaey aur usey apney dil mein rakha yahan tak ke jab uska Malik aaya to usney logon ki mojudgi mein aap ko salam kya, lekin aapney us se aeraz kya, usney kaee martaba aisey kya, yahan tak ke us aadmi ne aap mein narazi aur apney se be rukhi pehchan li , usney apney sathiyon se wajeh daryaft ki aur kaha : Allah ki qism ! main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko naraz mehsus karta hun lekin wajeh narazi malum nahin, unhoney bataya , aap bahar tashrif laye they aur aapney tumhara qubba dekha tha, wo aadmi apney qubbey ki taraf gaya aur usey gira kar zamin ke barabar kar diya, phir eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif laye to aapney us ( qubbey) ko na dekha to farmaya : ''qubbey ko kya hua?'' Sahaba ne arz kya, uskey Malik ne aap ki be rukhi ki ham se wajeh daryaft ki to ham ne usey bata diya, pas usney usey gira diya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sun lo! her imarat jiskey baghair guzaara ho sakta ho wo apney Malik ke liye wabal hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
5185,"Hazrat Abu-Hashim bin Utba bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey wasiyat kartey huey farmaya : ''tumharey liye itna maal jama karna hi kafi hai ke eik khaadim ho aur Allah ki raah mein (jihad karney ke liye) eik sawari ho.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Nasai , ibne-Maja , aur masaabeh ke baaz nuskhon mein abu-Hashim bin Utbd yani تاء ke bajaey daal ka zikr hai, aur ye tas-heef hai. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja w masaabeh."
5186,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' insan ko in teen chizon , rihaaish ke liye ghar , sattar dhaanpney ke liye kapdey aur roti pani ke siwa kisi chiz ka haq nahin.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5187,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi aaya aur usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey aisa amal bataeyn jab main wo amal kar lun to main Allah aur logon ka mehbub bin jaaun , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' duniya se be raghbat ho ja Allah tujh se mohabbat kerega aur jo kuch logon ke paas hai us se be raghbat ho ja to log tujh se mohabbat karengey .'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
5188,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik chatai par so gaey jab uthey to aap ke jism par us ( chatai (ke nishaanaat they, ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! agar aap hamen hukm farmaain to ham aap ke liye naram bistar tayyar kar den, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mera duniya se kya sarokaar, mein aur duniya to aisey hain jaisey koi sawar kisi darkht ke nichey saya hasil karney ke liye rukta hai aur phir kooch kar jata hai aur usey wahin chhod jata hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
5189,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey doston mein se wo momin merey nazdik ziyada qabile-rashk hai jiskey paas saazo saman kam ho, Namaz mein usey lazzat hasil hoti ho, apney rab ki ibadat khub achi tarah karta ho aur wo poshida haalat mein bhi uski itaat karta ho, logon mein mashhoor na ho, uski taraf ungliyan na uthti hun, uska rizq guzaara laaiq ho aur wo is par sabir ho.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik chutki bajaaii aur farmaya : ''uski maut jaldi aa gaee, usey roney waliyan kam hain aur uski meeras bhi kam hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
5190,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey rab ne mujhey pesh kaash! ki ke wo Makka ki wadi Bat'ha (ya Makka ke sang rezon) ko sona bana dey , maine kaha : rab ji ! nahin, balke mein chahta hun ke main eik roz pet bhar khaaun aur eik roz bhookaa rahun , jab main bhookaa rahun to terey huzur aajizi karun aur tera zikr karun, aur jab pet bhar kar khaaun to teri hamd bayan karun aur tera shukr ada karun .'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi ."
5191,"Hazrat Ubaid Allah bin Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jo shakhs is haal mein subh karey ke usey apney ehl w ayaal ke mutalliq koi khatra na ho aur wo tandurust ho, aur uskey paas eik din ka khana mojud ho to goya uskey liye tamam atraaf se duniya jama kar di gaee.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5192,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''kisi aadmi ne aisa koi bartan nahin bhara jo uskey pet se ziyada bura ho, insan ke liye chand luqmey hi kafi hain jo uski kamar sidhi rakh saken, agar ziyada khana zaroori hi ho to phir ( pet ka ( tihai hissey khaney ke liye, tihai pani ke liye aur tihai saans ke liye ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
5193,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko dakaar letey huey suna to farmaya : ''apna dakaar kam kar, kyonkey roze-qiyamat wo shakhs logon se bahut der tak bhooka rahega jo duniya mein khub sair ho kar khata tha.'' Sharahus-sunnah, aur Imam Tirmizi ne isi tarah riwayat kya hai. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah w Tirmizi ( ."
5194,"Hazrat Kab bin Ayaaz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' her ummat ke liye eik fitna ( aazmaaish w imtihan ( raha hai aur meri ummat ka fitna maal hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5195,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''insan ko roze-qiyamat bakri ke bachey ki tarah (zillat ke sath) pesh kya jaeyga, aur usey Allah ke huzur khada kya jaeyga to wo us se farmaeyga : maine tujhey ( hayaat w hawaas , sehat w aafiyat ( ata ki, maine tujhey khaadim mulaazim ata kiye aur) Anbiya w kutub nazil farma kar) tujh par inaam farmaya , to ne kya kya? wo arz kerega rab ji ! maine us ( maal ( ko jama kya aur usko badhaya aur jitna tha us se ziyada chhoda , to mujhey wapis bhej mein wo sara teri khidmat mein ley aata hun. usey kaha jaeyga : tum ne jo aagey bheja tha wo mujhey dikhao, to wo phir wohi kahega , maine usey jama kya, usey badhaya aur wo jitna tha us se ziyada usey chhoda , lihaza to mujhey wapis bhej mein wo sara teri khidmat mein la hazir karta hun, chunanche wo aisa ( bad qismat ( insan hoga jisney koi neki aagey nahin bheji hogi , usey jahannam ki taraf bhej diya jaeyga.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney usey zaeef qarar diya hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
5196,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roze-qiyamat bandey se nematon ke barey mein sab se pehley yun sawal kya jaeyga : kya ham ne terey jism ko durust nahin banaya tha, aur) kya ( ham ne tujhey thandey pani se sairab nahin kya tha ?'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5197,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roze-qiyamat insan ke qadam ( Allah ke darbar mein) barabar jamey rahengey yahan tak ke us se paanch chizon ke mutalliq na poochh liya jaey : uski umr ke mutalliq ke usney usey kin kamon mein khatam kya, uski jawani ke mutalliq ke usney usey kahan zaya kya, uskey maal ke mutalliq ke usney usey kahan se hasil kya aur usey kin masaarif mein kharch kya aur apney ilm ke mutabiq kitna amal kya ?'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
5198,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''tum surkh se behtar ho na siyah sey, magar ye ke tum us se taqwa ke zariey fazilat hasil karo.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
5199,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''banda duniya se be raghbati ikhtiyar karta hai to Allah uskey dil mein hikmat paida farma deta hai, us (hikmat) ko uski zaban par jari farma deta hai, duniya ka aeb, uski beemaariyaan aur uskey ilaj par usey baseerat ata farma deta hai aur usey us se sahih salaamat daarussalam (jannat) ki taraf nikal ley jata hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5200,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us shakhs ne falah pai jiskey dil ko Allah ne eman ke liye khalis kar diya, uskey dil ko) hasad w bughz waghera sey) salaamat rakha , uski zaban ko raast bhale hi banaya , uskey nafs ko mutmain banaya , uski tabiat ko mustaqeem banaya, uskey kanon ko ghor se ( haq ( sunney wala aur uski aankh ko) daleel ( dekhney wala banaya , kaan us chiz ke liye jisey dil mehfooz rakhta hai, qeef hain aur aankh mehal qarar w sabaat hai, aur us shakhs ne falah pai jisney apney dil ko muhafiz banaya .'' ( rawahu Ahmed w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5201,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum Allah azz-w-jall ko dekho ke wo bandey ko apni gunah ke bawajud duniya dey raha hai jis ( gunah ( ko wo pasand nahin karta to wo koi tadbeer hai.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''jab unhoney us chiz ko bhula diya jiskey zariey unhen samjhaya gaya tha to ham ne un par her chiz ke darwazey khol diye, yahan tak ke jab wo ata karda chizon par khush ho gaey to ham ne unhen achcha pakad liya, tab wo hairat mein pad gaey aur na-umeed ho gaey .'' rawahu Ahmed ."
5202,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ehle-suffa mein se eik aadmi faut ho gaya to usney eik Dinar chhoda to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' (ye deenar) eik dagh ( deney ke baais ( .'' raawi bayan kartey hain, phir doosra aadmi faut hua to usney do Dinar chhodey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( ye do Dinar ( do dagh ( deney ka baais ( hain.'' , ( rawahu Ahmed w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5203,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo apney mamu abu-Hashim bin Utba (Raziallahu anhu) ki iyaadat ke liye gaey to abu-Hashim (Raziallahu anhu) roney lagey, unhoney puchha : mamu jaan! kon si chiz aap ko rula rahi hai, kya koi takleef tumhen iztirab mein dal rahi hai ya duniya ki hirs? unhoney kaha, hergiz nahin, balke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen wasiyat farmaai thi lekin maine is par amal na kya, unhoney farmaya : wo (wasiyat) kya thi? unhoney kaha, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' tumharey liye itna maal jama karna hi kafi hai ke eik khaadim ho aur Allah ki raah mein jihad karney ke liye eik sawari ho.'' aur main khayal karta hun ke main ( maal ( jama kar chuka hun. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
5204,"Hazrat Umme-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aapko kya hai ke aap falan ki tarah (maal w mansab) talab nahin kartey? unhoney farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''tumharey aagey eik dushwaar ghaati hai jisey bhari wazan uthaney waley paar nahin kar sakengey.'' mein chahta hun ke main us ghaati (se guzarney) ke liye wazan halka rakhun. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5205,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya koi aisa shakhs hai jo pani par chalta ho lekin uskey paaon geeley na hotey hon?'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''duniya daar shakhs isi tarah hai, wo gunahon se mehfooz nahin reh sakta.'' in dono hadeeson ko Imam Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein riwayat kya hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5206,"Hazrat Juber bin Nafair (Raziallahu anhu) mursal riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri taraf ye wahi nahin ki gaee ke main maal jama karun aur tajiron mein se ho jaaun, balke meri taraf wahi ki gaee hai ke ''apney rab ki hamd ke sath tasbih bayan karen aur sajda karney walon mein se ho jaeyn, aur apney rab ki ibadat kartey rahen yahan tak ke aap wafat pa jaeyn.'' Sharahus-sunnah, aur abu-Nuem ne abu Muslim se huliya mein riwayat kya hai. ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah w fi huliya al-auliyaa ( ."
5207,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne halal tareeqey sey, maangney se bachney ke liye, apney ehl w ayaal par kharch karney ke liye aur apney padosi par meharbani karney ke liye duniya talab ki to wo roze-qiyamat Allah Taala se mulaqat kerega to uska chehra chaudahwin raat ke chaand ki tarah ( chamakta ( hoga. aur jis shakhs ne halal tareeqey sey, maal mein izafa karney ke liye , baham (aapas mein) fakhr karney ke liye aur riyaakaari ke liye duniya talab ki to wo Allah Taala se us haal mein mulaqat kerega ke wo is par naraz hoga.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5208,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak ye khair ke khazaney hain, un khazanon ki chabiyan hain, us bandey ke liye khushkhabri hai jisey Allah ne khair ke liye chaabi (kholney wala) bana diya aur shar ko band karney wala bana diya, aur us bandey ke liye halakat hai jisey Allah ne shar kholney wala aur khair ko band karney wala banaya .'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
5209,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab bandey ke kisi maal mein barkat na rakhi jaey to wo us maal ko pani aur mitti (yani taameer) par sirf karta hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
5210,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''taameeraat ke silsiley mein) irtikab ( haram se bacho , kyonkey wo kharabi ki asaas hai.'' dono riwayaat ko Imam Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein riwayat kya hai. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5211,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' duniya uska ghar hai jis ka koi ghar nahin, uska maal hai jis ka koi maal nahin, aur us ( duniya (ke liye wohi jama karta hai jo aql mand nahin .'' ( rawahu Ahmed w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5212,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko doran khutba farmatey huey suna : ''sharab tamam gunahon ka majmua hai, aurten shetan ke jaal hain, aur duniya ki mohabbat her gunah ki asal w buniyad hai.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' aurton ko peechey rakho jaisey Allah ne unhen peechey rakha .'' rawahu rizeen ."
5213,aur Imam Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein isey Hasan se mursal riwayat kya hai : ''duniya ki mohabbat tamam gunahon ki buniyad hai.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( .
5214,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey apni ummat ke mutalliq khahish nafs aur tool aarzu ka sab se ziyada andesha hai, kyonkey khahish nafs haq se rokti hai jabkey tool aarzu aakhirat bhula deti hai, aur ye duniya (ghair mehsus tareeqey sey) chali ja rahi hai jabkey aakhirat (usi tarah) chali aa rahi hai, aur dono mein se her eik ke talabgaar hain, tum duniya ke talabgaar na bano, amal kartey raho, kyonkey aaj tum daare-amal mein ho aur koi hisab nahin, aur kal daare-aakhirat mein hogey aur koi amal nahin hoga.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5215,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : duniya guzar rahi hai jabkey aakhirat aa rahi hai, aur dono mein se her eik ke talabgaar hain, tum aakhirat ke talabgaar bano aur duniya ke talabgaar na bano kyonkey aaj amal (ka waqt) hai aur hisab nahin jabkey kal hisab hoga aur amal nahin hoga.'' Bukhari ."
5216,"Hazrat Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik roz khutba irshad farmaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney khutbey mein farmaya : ''sun lo ! duniya eik hazir maal hai, nek bhi us se khata hai aur faajir bhi, sun lo ! aakhirat eik atal haqiqat hai, us waqt qadir matlab badshah (nek aur faajir ke darmiyan) faisla karega, sun lo ! khair mukammal taur par jannat mein hai aur sun lo ! shar mukammal taur par jahannam mein hai, aur sun lo ! amal kartey raho , tum Allah ki taraf se ( shar ke hone khof sey) dartey raho , aur jaan lo ke tumhen tumharey aamaal par pesh kiya jaeyga, jis shakhs ne zarra barabar neki ki hogi usey dekh lega aur jisney zarra barabar burai ki hogi wo bhi usey dekh lega .'' Imam Shafai ne isey riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Shafai."
5217,"Hazrat Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''logo ! be-shak duniya hazir maal hai, her nek aur faajir us se khata hai, aakhirat atal haqiqat aur sachcha wada hai, aadil qadir badshah us waqt faisla farmaeyga , wo is mein haq ko Sabit kar dega aur batil ko naapaid kar dega , aakhirat ke talabgaar bano, duniya ke talabgaar na banuo, be-shak her bachcha apni maa ke peechhey chalta hai.''  (rawahu Abu naeem fi huliya al-auliyaa)."
5218,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Suraj tulu hota hai to uskey dono kinaron par do farishtey aawaz detey hain, wo jinnon aur insanon ke siwa sari makhluq ko (apni aawaz) sunatey hain : logo ! apney rab ki taraf aao , jo (maal) thoda aur kafi ho wo us (maal) se behtar hai jo ziyada ho aur (Allah ki yad sey) ghafil kar dey.'' dono hadison ko Abu Naeem ne الحلیہ mein riwayat kiya hai. (rawahu Abu Naeem fi huliya al-auliyaa)."
5219,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) marfoo riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab faut honey wala faut hota hai to farishtey kehtey hain : usney (aamaal mein sey) aagey kya bheja hai? aur insan kehtey hain, usney (maal mein sey) peechhey kya chhoda hai? '' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5220,"Hazrat Imam Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke luqman ne apney bete se farmaya : ''bete ! be-shak logon se jis chiz ka wada kiya gaya hai wo un par daraz ho chala hai, aur wo aakhirat ki taraf tez chaley ja rahey hain, aur jab se to duniya mein aaya hai us waqt se to usey (aahista aahista) peechhey chhod raha hai aur aakhirat ki taraf pesh qadmi kar raha hai, be-shak wo ghar jiski taraf to safar kar raha hai, wo terey us ghar sey, jahan se to rawana hua hai, ziyada qarib hai.'' rawahu Rizeen."
5221,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya gaya, kon sa aadmi sab se behtar hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her saaf-dil, saf suthri baat karne wala.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, ham saf suthri baat karne wale ke mutalliq to jantey hain, saaf dil se kya murad hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo saaf aur paak jis par koi gunah hai na koi zulm aur na hi koi keena aur hasad.'' ( rawahu ibne-Maja aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5222,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chaar chizen aisi hain jab wo tum mein hon to phir agar tumhen duniya na bhi miley to koi harj aur muzaaeqa nahin, hifz, amanat , sachchey kalam , Husne-akhlaq aur (haram) khaney se perhez karna.'' (rawahu Ahmed aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5223,"Hazrat Imam Maalik se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mujhey hadees pahunchi hai ke Luqman Hakim se puchha gaya, jis maqam par ham aap ko dekh rahey hain us maqam par aap ko kon si baaton ne pahunchaya? unhoney farmaya : saf suthri baat karne wala , amanat ki adaegi aur fuzul baaton chiz ko chhod dena. rawahu Maalik."
5224,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aamaal (Allah ke huzur sifarish karney ke liye) aaeyngey, Namaz aaeygi, aur arz karegi , rab ji ! main Namaz hun, wo farmaeyga : to khair par hai, sadqa aaeyga , wo arz karega , rab ji ! main sadqa hun, wo farmaeyga : to khair par hai, phir roza aaeyga , wo arz kerega : rab ji ! main roza hun, wo farmaeyga : to khair par hai, phir isi tarah aamaal aatey jaeyngey, Allah Taala farmata jaeyga : to khair par hai, phir Islam aaeyga , wo arz karega : rab ji ! to salam hai aur main Islam hun, Allah Taala farmaeyga : to khair par hai, aaj mein teri wajeh se muwaakhiza (pakad) karunga aur teri wajeh se ata karunga , Allah Taala ne apni kitab mein farmaya : ''jo shakhs Islam ke ilawa koi aur Deen talash kerega to wo us se hergiz qubul nahin kiya jaeyga aur wo aakhirat mein nuqsan uthaney walon mein se hoga.'' rawahu Ahmed."
5225,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, hamara eik parda tha jis mein parindon ki taswiren thin (ye dekh kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aaisha ! isey badal dalo, kyonkey jab main isey dekhta hun to main duniya yad karta hun (mujhey duniya yad aa jati hai).'' rawahu Ahmed."
5226,"Hazrat Abu Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney arz kiya, mujhey mukhtasar si wasiyat farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab to Namaz padhey to aisey padh jaisey aakhiri Namaz ho, aisi baat na kar jiski wajeh se kal mazrat karni padey aur jo kuchh logon ke paas hai us se mukammal taur par na-umeed aur la-talluq ho ja.'' rawahu Ahmed."
5227,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey Yamen ki taraf bheja to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey wasiyat karney ke liye uskey sath bahar tashrif laye us waqt Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) sawar they, jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski sawari ke sath sath pedal chal rahey they, jab aap farigh huey to farmaya : ''Muaz mumkin hai ke tum is saal ke baad mujh se mulaqat na kar sako, shayad ke tum meri masjid aur meri qabr ke paas se guzro.'' Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki judai ki wajeh se ghabra kar roney lagey , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Madina ki taraf rukh pher kar farmaya : ''muttaqi log meri qurbat aur shafaat ke ziyada haq daar hain wo jo bhi hon aur jahan bhi hon.'' chaaron hadisen Imam Ahmed ne riwayat ki hain. rawahu Ahmed."
5228,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''Allah jisey hidayat deney ka irada farmata hai to uskey seeney ko Islam ke liye khol deta hai.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Noor jab seeney mein dakhil ho jata hai to Sina khul jata hai.'' arz kiya gaya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya uski koi alamat bhi hai jiskey zariey uska pata chal sakey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, dhokey ke ghar (duniya) se doori, hamesha ke ghar (aakhirat) ki taraf ruju aur maut aaney se pehley maut ki tayyari.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5229,Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Abu Khallad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum bandey ko dekho ke usey duniya se be-raghbati ata ki gaee hai aur wo kam bolne wala hai to uska qurb hasil karo kyonkey usey hikmat ata ki gaee hai.'' dono riwaayatein Imam Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein naqal ki hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan).
5230,Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Abu khallad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum bandey ko dekho ke usey duniya se be-raghbati ata ki gaee hai aur wo kam bolne wala hai to uska qurb hasil karo kyonkey usey hikmat ata ki gaee hai.'' dono riwaayatein Imam Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein naqal ki hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan).
5231,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bahut se bikhre baalon waley jinhen darwazon se dhakela jata hai agar wo Allah par qism utha ley to Allah usey puri farma deta hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5232,"Hazrat Musab bin Saad bayan kartey hain ke Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne khayal kiya ke usey apney se kam darja logon par (sakhaawat karney mein) fazilat aur bartari hasil hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey kamzor logon ki wajeh hi se tumhari madad ki jati hai aur unhi ki wajeh se tumhen rizq diya jata hai.'' Bukhari."
5233,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main (Mairaj ki raat) jannat ke darwazey par khada hua to dekha ke is mein ziyada tar dakhil honey waley miskin they, jabkey sahibe sarwat (daulat) rok liye gaey they, aur aag walon (yani kafiron) ke liye jahannam ka hukm dey diya gaya tha, aur main jahannam ke darwaze par khada hua aur dekha ke is mein janey walon ki aksariyat aurton ki thi .'' muttafaq aleh."
5234,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine jannat mein jhank kar dekha to is mein aksariyat fuqra ki thi, aur maine jahannam mein jhank kar dekha to maine dekha ke wahan aksariyat aurton ki hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5235,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Muhajir fuqra , roze-qiyamat maal-daaron se chaalis saal pehley jannat mein dakhil hongey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5236,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se guzra to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney paas bethey huey shakhs se farmaya : ''us (shakhs) ke mutalliq tumhari kya raey hai? '' usney kaha : moazziz logon mein se hai, Allah ki qism ! ye us laaiq hai ke agar kahin peghame nikah bhejey to uski shaadi kar di jaey, aur agar kahin sifarish karey to wo qubul ki jaey, raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh rahey, phir eik aadmi guzra to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''us shakhs ke mutalliq tumhari kya raey hai?'' usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ye shakhs gharib musalmanon mein se hai, ye us laaiq hai ke agar kahin peghame nikah bhejey to uski shaadi na ki jaey aur agar kahin sifarish karey to uski sifarish qubul na ki jaey aur agar baat karey to uski baat na suni jaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye (tanha) shakhs us shakhs jaisey logon se bhari zamin se behtar hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5237,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, aale Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do din mutawatir (lagataar) jau ki roti pet bhar kar nahin khai yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wafat pa gaey. muttafaq aleh."
5238,"Hazrat Saeed Maqbari (Raziallahu anhu) , Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke wo kuchh logon ke paas se guzrey unke samney bhuni hui bakri thi, unhoney unhen dawat di to unhoney usey khaney se inkar kar diya aur farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) duniya se tashrif ley gaey aur aapney pet bhar kar jo ki roti nahin khai. Bukhari."
5239,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo jau ki roti aur rangat badli hui charbi lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf gaey jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zireh Madina main eik Yahudi ke paas girwi thi, aapney us se apney ghar walon ke liye jau liye they, aur main (raawi) ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna : aale Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan Sham ke waqt na eik saa gehun hote the aur na eik saa koi aur anaj hota tha jabkey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nau-paak-biviyon thin. Bukhari."
5240,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap khajoor ki chatai par letey huey they aur aapney koi bistar waghera nahin bichhaya hua tha, aur us chatai ke nishaanaat aap ke pehlu par they, aur aapney chamdey ke takiye par tek lagai hui thi, jis mein khajoor ke darkht ke pattey bharey huey they, maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ke huzur dua farmaain ke wo aap ki ummat par faraakhi farmaai , kyonkey faarsiyon aur roomiyon par bahut nawazishat hain, halanke wo Allah ki ibadat nahin kartey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ibne khattab ! kya tum abhi tak usi maqam par ho? ye (kuffar) wo log hain ke unhen unki lazzaten is duniya ki zindagi mein jald ata kar di gaee hain.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''kya tum khush nahin ke unke liye duniya mein ho aur hamarey liye aakhirat mein.'' muttafaq aleh."
5241,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, meri sattar as-haabe-suffa se mulaqat hui hai, un mein se kisi eik aadmi par bhi badi chadar nahin thi, unke paas ya to eik-eik tehband tha ya eik chadar thi, unhoney uskey kinarey ko gardanon ke sath baandh rakha tha, un mein se kuch chadaren aisi thin jo nisf pindliyon tak pahunchti thin kuch ki takhnon tak pahunchti thin, aur wo usey apney haath ke sath ikhatta karta tha ke kahin uska sattar na khul jaey. Bukhari ."
5242,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi maal aur surat w jamaal mein apney se behtar shakhs ko dekhey to wo apney se kam tar shakhs ko dekh ley.'' aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : '' ( dunyawi umur (baton) mein) apney se kam tar shakhs ko dekho aur apney se behtar shakhs ko na dekho , kyonkey ye ziyada laaiq hai ke tum Allah ki un nematon ko haqeer na jano jo usney tum par inaam ki hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
5243,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' fuqra maal daaron se paanch so saal pehley jannat mein jaeyngey jo ke aadha din hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5244,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! mujhey miskeen zinda rakhna , miskeen hi faut karna aur mujhey miskinon ke giroh mein jama farmana .'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kyon ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kyonkey wo maal daaron se chaalis saal pehley jannat mein jaeyngey, Aaisha ! kisi miskeen ko khaali haath na modna chahey khajoor ka eik tukda ho, Aaisha! miskinon se mohabbat karna, unhen qarib rakhna chunanche roze-qiyamat Allah tujhey (apney ( qarib kerega.'' ( rawahu Tirmizi w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5245,"aur ibne-Maja ne abu Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey, miskinon ke giroh mein utha, tak riwayat kya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja ."
5246,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey apney zaeefon mein talash karo, tum apney un kamzoron hi ki wajeh se rizq diye jatey ya madad kiye jatey ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5247,"Hazrat Umayya bin Khalid bin Abdullah bin Usaid, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap Muhajir fuqra ki duaon ke zariey Fateh talab kya kartey they. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
5248,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi fajir shakhs ko nematon mein dekh kar is par rashk na karna kyonkey tum nahin jantey ke uski maut ke baad uskey sath kya sulook honey wala hai, uskey liye Allah ke yahan eik mohlik chiz hai jo maregi nahin.'' yani : jahannam. ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
5249,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''duniya momin ke liye qaid khana aur qehat hai, jab wo duniya se juda hota hai to wo qaid khaney aur qehat se juda ho jata hai.'' ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
5250,Hazrat Qatada bin Noman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah kisi bandey ko pasand farmata hai to usey duniya (ke maal w mansab) se bacha leta hai jaisey tum mein se koi apney mareez ko pani se bachata hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi.
5251,"Hazrat Mehmood bin labid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do chizen hain jinhen insan napasand karta hai, insan maut ko napasand karta hai, halanke maut mominon ke liye fitney se behtar hai, aur wo qillat maal ko napasand karta hai jabkey qillat maal ka hisab kam hai.'' rawahu Ahmed."
5252,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney arz kya, main aap se mohabbat karta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dekh lo tum kya keh rahey ho?'' usney arz kya, Allah ki qasam! main aap se mohabbat karta hun, usney teen martaba kaha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum (apney daawa mein) sachey ho to phir faqr w faaqa ka muqabla karney ke liye dhaal tayyar rakho kyonkey jo shakhs mujh se mohabbat karta hai to uski taraf faqr sailab ki raftaar se bhi ziyada tezi se aata hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
5253,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey Allah ki raah mein jitna daraya gaya hai itna kisi ko nahin daraya gaya, Allah ki raah mein jitni mujhey aziyat di gaee hai itni kisi ko aziyat nahin di gaee, mujh par tees din raat bhi guzrey hain ke merey aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye aisi koi chiz nahin thi jisey koi jandaar khata hai, albatta itni (qaleel) chiz thi jisey Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki baghal chupa leti thi .'' aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : is hadees ka maana ye hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka se bhag nikley they to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke sath they, aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bas itna sa khana tha jo wo apni baghal ke nichey rakhtey they. rawahu Tirmizi ."
5254,"Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bhook ki shikayat ki aur ham ne apney pet se kapda utha kar eik pathar bandha hua dikhaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney pet par do pathar bandhey huey dikhaye. Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5255,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhen bhook lagi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen eik eik khajoor ata farmaey. rawahu Tirmizi .
5256,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' do khaslatein jis shakhs mein hun Allah usey shakir, sabir likh deta hai, jo shakhs apney Deen ke mamley mein apney se ooper waley ko dekhta hai aur phir uski iqtida karta hai, aur duniya ke mamley mein wo apney se nichey waley ko dekhta hai aur Allah ne jo usko is par fazilat ata ki hai is par Allah ka shukr ada karta hai, to Allah usey shukr guzar sabr karney wala likh deta hai, aur jo shakhs apney Deen ke mamley mein apney se kam tar ko aur duniya ke mamley mein apney se bartar ko dekhta hai aur jo chiz usey nahin mili is par afsos karta hai to Allah usey shakir w sabir nahin likhta.'' rawahu Tirmizi. aur abu-Saeed se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''muhajrin ki faqir jamaat khush ho jaao ''(fazaailul-Quran) ke baab ke baad zikr ki gaee hai."
5257,"Hazrat abu Abdurrehman Habli bayan kartey hain, maine Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, eik aadmi ne un se sawal puchha : kya ham Muhajir fuqra mein se nahin? Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey farmaya : kya tumhari biwi hai jiskey paas tum raat basar kartey ho? usney kaha : ji haan! unhoney farmaya : kya terey rehney ke liye ghar hai? usney kaha : ji haan! unhoney farmaya : tum to maal daaron mein se ho, usney kaha : merey paas to eik khaadim bhi hai, unhoney farmaya : tum to badshah ho, Abdurrehman ne kaha, teen aadmi Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye, mein us waqt unke paas tha, unhoney kaha : abu Muhammad ! Allah ki qasam! hamarey paas kuch bhi nahin, koi kharcha hai na sawari aur na hi saaz w saman , unhoney unhen farmaya : tum kya chahtey ho? agar tum kuch chaho to tum hamarey paas aana, Allah ne tumharey liye jo muyassar farmaya wo ham tumhen ata karengey, aur agar tum chaho to ham tumhara maamla badshah se zikr karengey? aur agar tum chaho to sabr karo, kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Muhajir fuqra roze-qiyamat maal daaron se chaalis saal pehley jannat mein jaeyngey.'' unhoney kaha : ham sabr kartey hain aur ham koi chiz nahin maangengey. rawahu Muslim."
5258,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main masjid mein betha hua tha jabkey fuqra muhajrin ka bhi eik halqa laga hua tha. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to aap unke halqey mein shamil ho gaey, mein bhi uth kar unki taraf chala gaya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''fuqra muhajrin ko is baat ki basharat di jaey jis se unke chehrey khush ho jaeyn, kyonkey wo maaldaaron se chaalis saal pehley jannat mein jaeyngey.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine dekha ke unke chehrey chamakney lagey, aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, yahan tak ke maine tamanna ki ke main unke sath hota ya un mein se hota. rawahu Darmi ."
5259,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, merey khaleel ne mujhey saat chizon ke mutalliq hukm farmaya , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne miskinon se mohabbat karney aur unke qarib rehney ka mujhey hukm farmaya , aapney mujhey hukm farmaya ke main apney se kam tar ki taraf dekhun aur jo mujh se ( duniya ke lihaz sey) bartar hai uski taraf na dekhun , aapney mujhey sila rehmi ka hukm farmaya agar-che wo qata' rehmi karen, aapney mujhey hukm farmaya ke main kisi se koi chiz na maangun , aapney mujhey hukm farmaya ke main haq baat karun agar-che wo kadwi ho, aapney mujhey hukm farmaya ke main Allah ke) haq ke) barey mein kisi malamatgar ki malamat se nadaron, aur aapney mujhey hukm farmaya ke main ( لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قَوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللہِ ( kasrat se padha karun, kyonkey wo (kalmaat) arsh ke nichey khazanon mein se eik khazana hain.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
5260,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko duniya ki teen chizen pasand thin, khana, aurten aur khushbu , aap ko do chizen mil gaeen aur eik na mil saki , aap ko aurten ( paak biviyon (Raziallahu anhu) (aur khushbu mil gaee lekin (pet bhar) khana na mila.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
5261,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khushbu aur aurten merey liye pasandida bana di gaee hain, aur meri aakhon ki thandak Namaz mein hai.'' Ahmed, Nasai, aur ibn Jauzi ne ( حُبَّبَ إلَیَّ (ke baad) مِنَ الدُّنْیَا (ka izafa naqal kya hai. rawahu Ahmed w Nasai."
5262,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey Yamen ki taraf bheja to farmaya : ''ziyada naaz w nemat ki zindagi se bachna, kyonkey Allah ke) mukhlis ( bandey ziyada nemat guzran nahin hotey.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
5263,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ki taraf se milney waley thodey se rizq par razi ho jata hai to Allah uskey thodey amal se razi ho jata hai.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
5264,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs bhook mein mubtala hua ya kisi chiz ka zarurat mand hua aur usney usey logon se chupaey rakha to Allah azz-w-jall par haq hai ke wo usey saal bhar ke liye rizq halal ata farmaey.'' dono riwaayaton ko Imam Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein naqal kya hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
5265,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah apney us momin ayaal daar bandey ko pasand karta hai jo zarurat mand honey ke bawajud sawal nahin karta .'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
5266,"Hazrat Zaid bin Aslam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik roz umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne pani talab kya to unhen shehad mila pani pesh kya gaya, unhoney farmaya : ye to bahut achcha hai, lekin main Allah azz-w-jall ka farman sunta hun ke usney eik qom ko unki shehwaat par mayoob qarar detey huey farmaya : ''tum ne apni achi chizen duniya ki zindagaani mein hasil kar lein aur tum ne un se istifaada kar liya.'' main to darta hun ke hamari nekiyon ka sawab duniya hi main na dey diya jaey, lihaza unhoney usey na piya. rawahu rizeen."
5267,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Fateh khaibar se pehley kabhi bhi sair ho kar khajuren nahin khaain. Bukhari ."
5268,"Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik murabba shakal khat khincha aur eik khat (us murabba ke) wast mein us se bahar jata hua khincha aur kuch us wast waley khat ke pehlu mein chhotey-chhotey khat aur kheenchey aur farmaya : ''ye insan hai aur ye uski ajal ( maut ( hai, jo usey gherey huey hai aur jo bahar ki taraf nikal rahi hai ye uski ummid hai, aur ye chhotey chhotey khutoot pesh aamada haadisey hain, agar eik us se khata kar jata hai to ye ( doosra ( usey daboch leta hai, aur agar ye us se khata kar jata hai to ye usey daboch leta hai.'' Bukhari."
5269,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuch khat kheenchey to farmaya : ''ye ummid hai, aur ye uski maut hai, wo usi beech mein hota hai to ziyada qarib wala khat achcha us tak aa pahunchta hai.'' Bukhari."
5270,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''insan boodha ho jata hai lekin uski do chizen jawan rehti hain, maal ki hirs aur umr ki hirs.'' muttafaq aleh."
5271,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' boodhey shakhs ka dil do chizon ke barey mein jawan hi rehta hai : duniya ki mohabbat ke barey mein aur lambi khaahishon ke barey mein.'' muttafaq aleh."
5272,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne us shakhs se ( tauba na karney aur nek amal na karney ka ( uzr zaayel kar diya jiski ajal ko muakhkhar kya yahan tak ke usey saath saal tak pahuncha diya.'' Bukhari ."
5273,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar insan ke liye maal ki do waadiyaan hon to wo teesri talash karta hai, insan ke pet ko sirf (qabr ki) mitti hi bharegi, aur Allah tauba karney waley shakhs ki tauba qubul farmata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5274,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey jism ke kisi hissey ko pakad kar farmaya : ''duniya mein aisey raho goya tum eik pardesi ya raah geer ho aur apney aap ko ehle-quboor (murdon) mein se shumar karo.'' Bukhari ."
5275,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas se guzrey to main aur meri walida (apney makaan ke) kisi hissey ki lipaai kar rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abdullah! kya ho raha hai? ''maine arz kya, ham (makaan ke kisi) hissey ki marammat kar rahey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maamla ( maut (us se ziyada tez hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi ."
5276,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kabhi peshab kartey to mitti se tayammum kartey, mein arz karta , Allah ke Rasool ! pani to aap ke qarib hi hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''mujhey kya pata shayad ke main wahan tak na pahunch sakun .'' Sharahus-sunnah , aur ibne-Jozi ne kitab ''alwafa'' main usey riwayat kya hai. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
5277,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye insan hai aur ye uski maut hai.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna haath apni guddi ke paas rakha, phir khola to farmaya : ''aur wahan uski aarzuein hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5278,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney samney eik lakdi gaadi, eik uskey pehlu mein aur eik uskey door gaadi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ye kya hai? ''Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye insan hai aur ye ajal hai.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, mera khayal hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye aarzuein hain, wo aarzuein hasil karney ke liye koshish karta hai to uski aarzu ke pura honey se pehley usey maut aa jati hai.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
5279,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ki umr saath aur sattar saal ke darmiyan hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
5280,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ki umrein saath aur sattar saal ke darmiyan hain, aur us (saath, sattar) se tajawuz karney waley un mein se kam hain.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja. aur Abdullah bin shikhkhir se marwi (bayan) hadees ( baab iyaada al-mareez) mein zikr ho chuki hai."
5281,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' is ummat ki pehli salaah ( aakhirat ka ( yaqin aur duniya se be raghbati hai, jabkey iska awwal fasad bukhl aur (la-mehdud) aarzuein hain.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
5282,"Hazrat Sufiyan Sauri (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : '' mota, jhota kapda pehanney aur rookha-sookha khaney ka naam duniya se be raghbati nahin, balke aarzuon ka kam hona duniya se be raghbati hai.'' ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
5283,"Hazrat Zaid bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, un se puchha gaya, duniya se be raghbatii se kya murad hai? unhoney farmaya : halal kamai aur ummeed ka kam hona. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5284,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah aisey maaldaar ko pasand farmata hai jo perhezgar, gum naam ho.'' rawahu Muslim. aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''hasad sirf do aadmiyon par hai, (baab fazaaile-Quran) mein bayan ho chuki hai."
5285,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! kon sa aadmi behtar hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jiski umr daraz ho aur uska amal achcha (yani Quran w sunnat ke mutabiq ( ho.'' us shakhs ne arz kya, sab se bura shakhs kon hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jiski umr daraz ho aur uska amal bura ho.'' rawahu Ahmed w Darmi ."
5286,"Hazrat Ubaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do aadmiyon ke darmiyan bhai-chaara qaaim kya, un mein se eik Allah ki raah mein Shahid kar diya gaya, phir doosra uskey taqriban eik haftey baad faut ho gaya, Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski Namaz janaza padhi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne uskey liye kya dua ki ?'' unhoney arz kya, ham ne Allah se dua ki ke wo uski maghfirat farmaai , is par rehem farmaai aur usey uskey sathi se milaaey . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uski wo namazein jo usney uski namazon ke baad padhein wo kahan gaeen? aur usney uskey baad jo amal kiye wo kahan gaey ?'' ya farmaya : '' usney uskey baad jo rozey rakhey to wo kahan gaey ?'' un dono ke beech to zamin w aasman ke beech fasley se ziyada fasla hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
5287,"Hazrat abu Kabsha Anmari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''teen khaslatein hain, main un par qism uthata hun aur main tumhen eik hadees bayan karta hun, tum usey yad kar lo, wo chizen jin par main qism uthata hun ye hain : sadqa karney se bandey ka maal kam nahin hota, jis bandey ki haq talfi ki jaey aur wo is par sabr karey to uskey badley mein Allah uski izzat mein izafa farmata hai, aur banda jab kisi se sawal karta hai to Allah usey faqr mein mubtala kar deta hai, rahi wo baat jo main tumhen bataaney ja raha hun usko khub yad rakhna .'' pas farmaya : '' duniya chaar qism ke logon ke liye hai : eik wo banda jisey Allah ne maal aur ilm ata kya ho aur wo us ( ilm (ke barey mein apney rab se darta ho, sila rehmi karta ho aur wo us ( ilm (ke mutabiq Allah ki khatir amal karta ho, ye sab se afzal darja hai. eik wo banda jisey Allah ne ilm diya ho lekin usey rizq na diya ho, aur wo niyat ka achcha hai, wo kehta hai : agar merey paas maal hota to main bhi falan ( maaldaar ( shakhs ki tarah kharch karta , un dono ke liye ajr barabar hai, aur eik wo banda hai jisey Allah ne maal ata kya lekin ilm nahin diya to wo ilm ke baghair apney maal ki wajeh se be raah rawi ka shikar ho jata hai, aur wo na to apney rab se darta hai aur na sila rehmi karta hai aur na hi usey haq ke mutabiq kharch karta hai, ye shakhs intehai burey darjey par hai, aur eik wo banda hai jisey Allah ne maal diya na ilm, wo kehta hai : agar merey paas maal hota to main bhi falan shakhs ki tarah amal (yani kharch) karta, wo sirf niyat hi karta hai jabkey dono ka gunah barabar hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees sahih hai. waah Tirmizi ."
5288,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah Taala jab kisi bandey ke sath bhalai ka irada karta hai to wo usey (itaat waley) kamon par laga deta hai.'' arz kya gaya : Allah ke Rasool! wo usey kis tarah kaam par lagata hai? farmaya : ''maut se pehley usey Saleh amal karney ki tofiq ata farma deta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi.
5289,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''daana shakhs wo hai jisney apney nafs ka muhaasba kya aur maut ke baad ke liye amal kiye, aur kam aql shakhs wo hai jisney apney nafs ko khaaish ke tabey kya aur Allah par ummid baandh li (ke wo ghafoor w raheem) hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
5290,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke eik sahabi se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : ham eik majlis mein they ke achcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur aap ke sar par pani (yani ghusl) ke asraat they, ham ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! ham aap ko khush dekh rahey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' theek hai.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, phir logon ne maal daari ke mutalliq ghor w khoz karna shuru kar diya ( kya wo jayez hai ya najaaiz ? ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah azz-w-jall se darta hai uskey liye maal daari mein koi muzaaeqa nahin, taqwa waley shakhs ke liye sehat, maaldaari se behtar hai, aur haqeeqi khushi nematon mein se hai.'' (sahih ( rawahu Ahmed ."
5291,"Hazrat Sufiyan Sauri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maazi mein maal naa-pasandida chiz thi, jabkey aaj wo momin ki dhaal hai, aur farmaya : agar (hamarey paas) Dinar na hotey to ye badshah hamen be-waqat samajhtey, aur farmaya : jis shakhs ke haath mein maal ho wo usey kaar-aamad banaey ( zaya na karey ( kyonkey ye aisa door hai ke agar wo zarurat mand hua to wo pehla shakhs hoga jo ( husoole-duniya ke liye ( apna Deen bech dalega , aur farmaya : halal fuzul kharchi ka mutahammil nahin ho sakta. zaeef mardud , ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
5292,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat manadi karney wala manadi kerega : 60 saala log kahan hain?'' aur ye (saath saal) wo umr hai jo Allah Taala ne farmaya : ''kya ham ne tumhen umr ata nahin ki thi, jisney nasihat pakadni thi wo nasihat pakadta, aur tumharey paas aagah karney waley bhi aaye.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
5293,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Banu Azra ke teen aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur unhoney Islam qubul kar liya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kon hai jo unke (khaney peeney ki) mujh se zimmedaari utha ley?'' Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : main, chunanche wo ( teeno ( unhen ke paas they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik lashkar rawana kya to un mein se eik us lashkar ke sath ho gaya aur wo Shahid ho gaya, phir aapney eik lashkar rawana kya to doosra shakhs uskey sath gaya to wo bhi Shaheed ho gaya, phir teesra shakhs apney bistar par faut ho gaya, raawi bayan kartey hain, Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine ( khuwab mein) teeno ko jannat mein dekha aur bistar par wafat pane-waley ko unke aagey dekha, jo baad mein Shahid hua tha wo uskey sath tha jabkey pehley Shahid honey wala shakhs us doosrey ( Shahid (ke sath tha, chunanche us se mujhey ishkal paida hua to maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska tazkira kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumko us se kon si chiz ajeeb lagi? Allah ke yahan us momin se afzal koi shakhs nahin jisey Islam mein Allah Taala ki tasbih w takbir aur tahleel ( '' لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ '' ( kehney ke liye lambi umr di jaey. rawahu Ahmed ."
5294,"Hazrat Muhammad bin abi Umaira (Raziallahu anhu) jo ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sahabi they, un se riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : agar banda apney yome-paidaish se lekar boodha ho kar marney tak Allah ki itaat mein sajda-rez rahey to wo roze-qiyamat usko bhi haqeer samjhega aur wo aarzu kerega ke kaash! usey duniya mein dobara bhej diya jaey taake wo ajr w sawab mein izafa kar sakey.'' dono riwayaat ko Imam Ahmed ne naqal kya hai. rawahu Ahmed ."
5295,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ke sattar hazar afrad hisab ke baghair jannat mein jaeyngey, ye wo log hain jo na dam-jhaad karatey hain aur na badshigooni letey they aur wo apney rab par tawakkul kartey they.'' muttafaq aleh."
5296,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to farmaya : '' mujh par ummaten pesh ki gaeen , chunanche eik Nabi guzrey unke sath eik aadmi tha, eik aur Nabi they aur unke sath do aadmi they, aur eik aur Nabi they unke sath chand aadmi they, jabkey kisi Nabi ke sath koi eik bhi nahin tha, maine eik bada giroh dekha jo ufuq tak phela hua tha, maine ummid ki ke ye meri ummat hogi lekin mujhey bataya gaya ke ye Musa (Alaihissalam) apni qom ke sath hain, phir mujhey kaha gaya, dekho , maine bahut bada giroh dekha jo ufuq tak phela hua tha, mujhey kaha gaya is taraf ( daain , baeyn) dekho, maine bahut bada giroh dekha jo ufuq par phela hua tha, mujhey bataya gaya ke ye aap ki ummat, aur unke sath unke aagey sattar hazar hain jo hisab ke baghair jannat mein jaeyngey, ye wo log hain jo ke badshigooni letey they na dam-jhaad karatey they aur na hi daaghtey they aur wo sirf apney rab par tawakkul kartey they.'' itney mein ukaasha bin Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) ne khadey ho kar arz kya, Allah se dua farmaain ke wo mujhey un mein shamil farmaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah! usko un mein se kar dey.'' phir eik aur aadmi khada hua aur usney arz kya, Allah se dua farmaain ke wo mujhey bhi un mein kar dey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' is mein ukaasha tujh se sabqat ley gaya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5297,"Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Momin ka maamla bhi ajeeb hai, uska her maamla uskey liye baaise-khair hai, aur ye chiz sirf momin ke liye khas hai, agar usey koi nemat muyassar aati hai to wo shukr karta hai aur ye uskey liye behtar hai, aur agar usey koi takleef pahunchti hai to wo sabr karta hai aur ye bhi uskey liye behtar hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5298,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qawi momin, zaeef momin se behtar hai neez wo Allah ko ziyada pasand hai, aur sab (mominon) mein khair hai, to apney liye nafa bakhsh chiz ke liye mehnat w koshish kar aur Allah se madad talab kar aur aajizi w susti na kar, aur agar tujhey koi nuqsan pahunchey to aisey na kaho : agar main (is tarah, is tarah) karta to is tarah, is tarah hota, balke aisey kaho : Allah ne muqaddar kya aur jo usney chaha so kya, kyonkey ( lafz ( ''agar '' amal shetan kholta hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5299,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''agar tum Allah par is tarah tawakkul karo jis tarah is par tawakkul karney ka haq hai, to wo tumhen is tarah rizq faraham karey jis tarah wo parindon ko rizq faraham karta hai, wo subh ke waqt bhookey nikaltey hain aur Sham ke waqt pet bhar kar wapis aatey hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
5300,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logo! her wo chiz jo tumhen jannat ke qarib kar dey aur tumhen jahannam se door kar dey main uskey mutalliq hukm dey chuka hun, aur her wo chiz jo tumhen jahannam ke qarib kar dey aur tumhen jannat se door kar dey main us se tumhen mana kar chuka hun, be-shak roohul-ameen, aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai, be-shak roohul-qudus ne merey dil mein ye baat dali ke koi nafs apna rizq pura kiye baghair faut nahin hoga, sun lo! Allah se daro aur achey tareeqey se rizq talash karo aur rizq ki takheer tumhen is baat par aamada na karey ke tum Allah ki nafarmani ke sath usey talab karo, kyonkey Allah ke yahan jo (in'aamaat) hain wo to mehaz uski itaat ke zariey hi hasil kiye ja saktey hain.'' Sharahus-sunnah , Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan , albatta Imam Behaqi ne ( '' وَاِنَّ رُوْحَ الْقُدُسِ '' (ka zikr nahin kya. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
5301,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''duniya se be raghbati, halal ko haram karney aur maal zaya karney ka naam nahin, balke duniya se be raghbati ye hai ke jo kuch terey haath mein hai wo us chiz sey, jo Allah ke haathon mein hai, ziyada qabile-aitimad na ho, aur ye ke na ho to musibat ke sawab mein jab to is mein mubtala kar diya jaey, raghbat karney wala ke wo ( musibat ( tujhey na pahunchti.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja , Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, aur Amr bin Waqid raawi munkire-Hadees hai. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
5302,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik roz main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey (sawari par betha hua) tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ladkey ! to Allah (ke ehkam) ki hifazat kar , Allah teri hifazat farmaeyga , to Allah  (ke huqooq) ka khayal rakh , to usey apney samney paeyga , aur jab to sawal karey to sirf Allah se kar , jab to madad talab karey to sirf Allah se madad talab kar , aur jaan ley ke agar puri ummat bhi jama ho kar tujhey kuchh faeyda pahunchana chahey to wo tujhey us se ziyada kuchh faeyda nahin pahuncha sakti jo Allah ne terey liye likh diya hai, aur agar wo tujhey nuqsan pahunchaney ke liye jama ho jaey to wo tujhey us se ziyada kuchh nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakti jo Allah ne terey liye likh diya hai, qalam utha liye gaey aur sahifey khushk ho gaey.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
5303,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''insan ki farmanbardari isi mein hai ke wo apney barey mein Allah ki qaza aur qadr par razi ho, insan ki bd-naseebi hai ke wo Allah se khair talab karna tarak kar dey aur insan ki bd-naseebi hai ke wo apney barey mein Allah ki qaza aur qadr par razi na ho.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
5304,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Najad ki taraf jihad kiya, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wapis aaye to wo bhi aap ke sath wapis aaye , Sahaba kiram ko ghaney kante-daar darakhton ki wadi mein do-pehar ko neend (qailula) ne aa liya , chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (aaram ki gharz sey) yahan padaaw dala aur Sahaba kiram darakhton ke saye ki talash mein alag alag ho gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne keekar ke darkht ke nichey padaaw dala aur apni talwaar us (darkht (ke sath latka di, aur ham thodi der ke liye so gaey, achcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein bulaney lagey , ham ne dekha ke eik Erabi (dehati) (dehati) aap ke paas hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usney , mujh par meri talwaar soont li jabkey main us waqt aaram kar raha tha main bedaar hua to talwaar uskey haath mein soonti hui thi, usney kaha : tujhey mujh se kon bachaeyga? maine teen martaba kaha : ''Allah (bachaeyga).'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski koi sarzanish nahin ki aur aap beth gaey. muttafaq aleh."
5305,"Aur Abu-Bakar ismaaeeli ne apni sahih mein yun riwayat ki hai, usney kaha : tujhey mujh se kon bachaeyga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ! talwaar uskey haath se gir gaee, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne talwaar pakad kar farmaya : ''tujhey mujh se kon bachaeyga?'' usney arz kiya : aap behtar pakadney waley hain (yani maaf kar den), aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum gawahi detey ho ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur ye ke main Allah ka Rasool hun?'' usney kaha : nahin, lekin main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye ehad karta hun ke main aap se na to qitaal karunga aur na aap se qitaal karney walon ka sath dunga, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska raasta chhod diya (usey janey diya), wo (dehaati) apney sathiyon ke paas aaya aur kaha : main behtareen shakhs ke paas se tumharey paas aaya hun. kitab al-humaidi aur riyaaz saliheen mein isi tarah hai. (rawahu fi Riyaaz saliheen w al-Behaqi fi dalaeyl النبوۃ) ."
5306,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main eik aisi aayat janta hun ke agar log is par amal karen to wo unke liye kafi ho jaey : ''jo shakhs Allah se dar jaey to wo uskey liye (tamam mushkilat sey) nikalney ki raah paida farma dega aur usey aisi jagah se rizq faraham karey jiskey barey mein usey weham aur guman bhi na tha.'' rawahu Ahmed, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
5307,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey ye aayat sikhai : ''be-shak main hi rizq ata karney wala, quwat aur taqat wala hun.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
5308,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein do bhai they, un mein se eik Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hota tha jabkey doosra karobar kiya karta tha, karobar karney waley ne apney bhai ki Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se shikayat ki, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shayad ke tumhen isi wajeh se rizq diya jata hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees sahih gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5309,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak insan ke dil ka her wadi mein hissey hai, jo shakhs apney dil ko tamam hisson ke peechey lagata hai to Allah ko uski parwah nahin chahey (chaahe) wo usey kisi bhi wadi mein halak kar dey , aur jo shakhs Allah par tawakkul karta hai to wo tamam hisson se kifaayat kar jata hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
5310,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey rab ne farmaya : agar merey bandey meri itaat karen to main raat ke waqt un par barish barsaaoon aur din ke waqt un par Suraj nikaalun aur unhen garaj ki aawaz bhi na sunaao.'' rawahu Ahmed.
5311,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi apney ehal aur ayaal ke paas gaya, jab usney unki (bhook ki) zarurat dekhi to wo (vinamarta aur inkisari karney ke liye) sehra (registaan) ki taraf chala gaya, jab uski ehliya ne dekha to wo chakki ki taraf gaee to usey durust kiya aur tandoor ki taraf gaee aur usey jalaayaa , phir us aurat ne dua ki, aey Allah ! hamein rizq ata farma, usney dekha ke achcha tab (aatey sey) bhar chuka hai, raawi bayan kartey hain, wo tandoor ki taraf gaee to usey bhi (rotiyon sey) bhara hua paya , raawi bayan kartey hain, shohar wapis aaya to usney kaha, kya merey baad tumhen koi chiz mili hai? ehliya ne kaha : ji haan ! hamarey rab ki taraf sey, wo chakki ki taraf gaya (taa ke usey dekhey) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska zikr kiya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar wo us (chakki ke paat) ko na uthata to wo roze-qiyamat tak chalti rehti.'' rawahu Ahmed."
5312,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yaqeenan rizq bandey ko is tarah talash karta hai jis tarah uski maut usey talash karti hai.'' (rawahu Abu Nuaim fi Huliya al-Auliyaa)."
5313,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, goya main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekh raha hun ke aap Anbiya (Alaihissalam) mein se eik Nabi ka waqia bayan kar rahey hain, unki qom ne unhen maara aur lahu-luhaan kar diya aur wo apney chehrey se khoon saaf kar rahey hain aur farma rahey hain, aey Allah ! meri qom ki maghfirat farma , kyonkey wo shuoor nahin rakhtay. muttafaq aleh."
5314,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yaqeenan Allah tumhari Suraton aur amwaal ko nahin dekhta, balke wo tumharey dilon aur aamaal ko dekhta hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5315,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : main (doosrey) tamam sharikon ke muqabley mein shirk se sab se ziyada be-niyaz hun, jo koi aisa amal karey jis mein wo merey sath merey ilawa kisi aur ko bhi shareek karey to main usko uskey shirk samet chhod deta hun.'' eik aur riwayat mein hai : ''main us (amal karney waley) se bezar hun, wo (amal) usi ke liye hai jis ke liye usney kiya hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5316,"Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs shohrat ki khatir koi amal karta hai to (roze-qiyamat) Allah us shakhs ko (logon ke samney) zaleel farmaeyga (ke usney is niyat se amal kiya tha) aur jo dikhlaao karta hai to Allah usey (logon ko) dikhla dega (ke ye shakhs riya-kaar hai).'' muttafaq aleh."
5317,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya gaya, aap bataeyn , eik aadmi neki ka kaam karta hai, is par log uski tareef kartey hain, eik dusri riwayat mein hai, is par log usey pasand kartey hain, (us ka kya hukm hai?) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye momin ke liye peshgi basharat hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5318,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed bin Abi Fazala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah logon ko roze-qiyamat , jis mein koi shak nahin, (hisab ke liye) jama farmaeyga to eik aelan karney wala aelan kerega : jisney kisi aisey amal mein , jisey usney akeley Allah ke liye kiya tha, shareek banaya to wo apna sawab , Allah ke ilawa kisi aur se talab karey, kyonkey Allah (doosrey) tamam sharikon ke muqabley mein shirk se sab se ziyada be-niyaz hai.'' rawahu Ahmed."
5319,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs apney amal ke mutalliq logon ko sunata hai to Allah uskey mutalliq apni makhluq ke kanon tak suna deta hai aur wo usey haqeer aur zaleel kar deta hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan).
5320,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ki niyat talabe-aakhirat ho to Allah uskey dil ko ghani kar deta hai, aur uskey mamley ko ikhatta farma deta hai aur duniya zaleel ho kar uskey paas chali aati hai, aur jis shakhs ki niyat talabe-duniya ho to Allah uski peshani par faqr (garibi) sabt farma deta hai, uskey mamley ko muntashir kar deta hai aur duniya usey itni hi milti hai jitni Allah ne uskey liye likh di hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5321,Hazrat Imam Darmi ne usey Aban ki sanad se Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Darmi.
5322,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! is beech mein ke main apney ghar main apni jaey Namaz par hota hun to achcha eik aadmi merey paas aata hai mujhey wo apni haalat achchhi lagti hai jis mein wo mujhey dekhta hai, (kya ye bhi riya kaari hai?) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Huraira ! Allah tum par rehem farmaai , tumharey liye dugna ajr hai, poshida ka ajr aur zahir ka ajr.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5323,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aakhiri zamaney mein kuchh aisey log zahir hongey jo Deen ke badley mein duniya talab karengey , wo logon ko khush karney ke liye bakri ki khaal pahneingey, unki zabanen (yani guftgu) cheeni se ziyada meethi hogi, aur unke dil bhediyon ke dilon jaisey hongey, Allah farmata hai, wo dhokey mein mubtala hain (ke main unhen mohlat dey raha hun) ya wo merey khilaf himmat kartey hain, main apni qism uthata hun ke main aisey logon par unhi mein se eik fitna barpa karunga ke wo unke haleem (aql-mand aur burdbar (samajhdar) shakhs ko bhi hairaan chhod dega.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5324,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah tabarak w taala ne farmaya : ''maine eik aisi makhluq paida ki hai ke unki zabanen cheeni se ziyada sheereen aur unke dil eilwey se ziyada kadwe hain, main apni zaat ki qism uthata hun ! main unhen eik fitney mein mubtala karunga ke wo unke haleem (aql-mand aur burdbar (samajhdar) shakhs ko bhi hairaan chhod dega, kya wo meri wajeh se dhokey mein mubtala huey hain ya merey khilaf himmat kartey hain?'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5325,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak her chiz ke liye raghbat aur khushi hoti hai aur her raghbat aur khushi ke liye zauf aur susti bhi hoti hai, agar us raghbat rakhney waley ne darmiyaanaa rah ikhtiyar ki aur ifraat se ehtiraaz kiya to uski (kamiyabi ki) ummid rakho aur agar uski taraf ungliyan uthai jaeyn (us ki mash'hoori ho jaey) to usey shumar na karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5326,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi aadmi ke liye yehi shar kafi hai ke uskey Deen ya duniya ke mamley mein uski taraf ungliyan uthai jaeyn (us ki shohrat ho jaey) magar wo shakhs jisey Allah mehfooz rakhey.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5327,"Hazrat Abu-Tameema (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Safwan (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke sathiyon ke paas mojud tha aur Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) unhen waaz aur nasihat farma rahey they, unhoney puchha : kya aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kuchh suna hai? unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs shohrat ki khatir koi amal karta hai to roze-qiyamat Allah usko ruswa kerega (ke ye us niyat se amal karta tha) aur jo apni jaan ko mashaqqat mein daalta hai to Allah roze-qiyamat usey mashaqqat mein mubtala kar dega.'' unhoney kaha : hamein wasiyat farmaain : unhoney farmaya : insan ke jism se uska pet sab se pehley kharab hota hai, lihaza jo shakhs istataat rakhta ho ke wo sirf halal hi khaye ga to usey aisey hi karna chahiye, aur jo shakhs istataat rakhey ke uskey aur jannat ke darmiyan eik chullu khoon, jo usney najaaiz bahaya ho wo haael (rukawat) na ho to wo zarur najaaiz khoon bahaney se bachey. Bukhari."
5328,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki masjid ki taraf aaye to unhoney Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qabr ke paas rotaa hua dekh kar un se puchha : tumhen kon si chiz rulaa rahi hai? unhoney farmaya : mujhey wo chiz rulaa rahi hai jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni thi, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''maamuli si riya kaari bhi shirk hai, aur jis shakhs ne merey kisi dost se dushmani rakhi to wo shakhs Allah ke sath jang karney ke liye maidan mein utar aaya, be-shak Allah aisey nek , muttaqi aur gum naam logon ko pasand karta hai ke jab wo ghayeb hon to unhen talash na kiya jata ho aur agar mojud hon to unhen bulaya nahin jata aur na unhen qarib kiya jata hai. unke dil hidayat ke chiragh hain, wo her qism ke gard aur ghubar se door hain.'' (kisi fitney ka shikar nahin hotey), (rawahu ibne-Maja aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5329,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak banda jab elaniya Namaz padhta hai to achchhey tareeqey se padhta hai aur tanhai mein Namaz padhta hai to bhi achchhey tareeqey se padhta hai, Allah Taala farmata hai : ye mera banda mukhlis hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
5330,Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aakhiri daur mein kuchchh aisey log hongey ke wo zahiri taur par dost hongey jabkey batni taur par dushman hongey.'' arz kiya gaya : Allah ke Rasool ! ye kis tarah hoga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye eik doosrey se raghbat (yani mafad) aur eik doosrey se khof (yani nuqsan) ke peshe-nazar hoga.'' rawahu Ahmed.
5331,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs dikhlaao ki khatir Namaz padhta hai to usney shirk kiya, jo shakhs dikhlaao ki khatir roza rakhta hai to usney shirk kiya, aur jo shakhs dikhlaao ki khatir sadqa karta hai to usney shirk kiya. ''dono hadison ko Imam Ahmed ne riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Ahmed."
5332,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo roney lagey , un se puchha gaya, tumhen kon si chiz rulaa rahi hai? unhoney kaha : wo chiz jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zabani suni , maine usey yad kiya to usney mujhey rulaa diya, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''mujhey apni ummat ke barey mein shirk aur makhfi (chhipi hui) khahish ka andesha hai.'' raawi bayan karta hai, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap ke baad aap ki ummat shirk karegi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, albatta wo Suraj ki chaand ki puja nahin karengey aur na hi pathar aur sanam ki, balke wo apney aamaal ka dikhlaao karengey , aur makhfi khahish ye hai ke un mein se koi rozey ki haalat mein subah kerega, lekin uski khaahishat mein se koi khahish uskey samney aa jaeygi to wo apna roza tod dega.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5333,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye to ham Masih dajjaal ke barey mein baat cheet kar rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen us chiz ke mutalliq na bataaun jis ka mujhey , tumharey mutalliq , Masih dajjaal se bhi ziyada andesha hai? ''ham ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! zarur bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shirke-khafi, wo ye hai ke eik aadmi Namaz padh raha hai aur jab wo dekhta hai ke koi shakhs mujhey dekh raha hai to wo (usey dikhaney ke liye) apni Namaz lambi kar deta hai (aahista aahista lambi qirat ke sath ziyada waqt lagata hai).'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
5334,"Hazrat Mehmood bin Labid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey tumharey mutalliq shirke-asghar ka sab se ziyada andesha hai.'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! shirke-asghar se kya murad hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''riya kaari.'' aur Imam Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein ye izafa naqal kiya hai : ''jis roz Allah bandon ko unke aamaal ki jaza dega to wo un (riyakaron) ko farmaeyga : unhi ki taraf chaley jaao jin ko tum duniya mein (apney aamaal) dikhaya kartey they, dekho kya tum unke paas jaza aur khair aur bhalai paatey ho?'' (rawahu Ahmed aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5335,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar koi aadmi kisi aisi chattan mein koi amal karta hai jis ka koi darwaza aur roshan daan nahin, to uska ye amal jaisa bhi ho logon par aashkar (zahir) ho jata hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5336,"Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ki koi nek ya bad khaslat chhupi hui ho to Allah us se koi alamat zahir farma dega jis se wo pehchana jaeyga.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5337,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey is ummat ke her munafiq ka andesha hai kyonkey wo baat hikmat ke sath karta hai jabkey amali taur par zulm karta hai.'' Imam Behaqi ne teeno hadise Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5338,"Hazrat Muhajir bin Habib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ka irshad hai : main daana (samajhdar insan) ke sarey kalam ko qubul nahin karta , lekin main uski niyat aur uskey iraday ko qubul karta hun, agar uski niyat aur uska irada meri itaat mein hai to main uski khamoshi ko apney liye hamd aur waqar qarar dey deta hun agar-che usney kalam na kiya ho.'' rawahu Darmi."
5339,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar tum (nafarmanon ke azab ke mutalliq) jaan lo jo main janta hun to tum ziyada ro'o aur kam hanso.'' Bukhari."
5340,"Hazrat Umme- Ala Ansaariya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! main nahin janta , Allah ki qism ! main nahin janta jabkey main Allah ka Rasool bhi hun ke merey sath aur tumharey sath kya sulook kiya jaeyga?'' Bukhari."
5341,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey samney jahannam ki aag pesh ki gaee to maine is mein Bani-Israel ki eik aurat ko uski eik billi ki wajeh se azab mein mubtala dekha, usney usey baandh rakha tha, usney usey na khud khilaya aur na usey chhoda ke wo kide-makode kha sakey usi haal wo bhooki mar gaee, aur maine Amr bin Aamir Khuzaai ko dekha ke wo jahannam main apni antadiyaan ghaseet raha tha, aur wo pehla shakhs hai jisney buton ke naam par janwer chhodney ki rasm ejaad ki.'' rawahu Muslim."
5342,"Hazrat Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghabrahat ke aalim mein merey paas tashrif laye, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, Arbon ke liye us shar ke sabab tabahi hai jo ke qarib pahunch chuki hai? aaj yajooj Majuj ka band is qadr khol diya gaya.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni do ungliyon, angoothey aur angusht shahadat se halqa banaya, Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham halak kar diye jaeyngey jabkey Saleh log ham mein mojud hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan , jab fisq (nafarmani) aur fujoor (buraai) ziyada ho jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5343,"Hazrat abu Aamir ya abu Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''meri ummat mein kuch aisey log hongey jo khaz (halki qism ka resham) aur aam resham, sharab aur aalaat mosiqi (musical instruments) ko halal samjhengey, aur kuch log pahad ke daman ki taraf utrengey unke sath unke maweshi aaeyngey, eik aadmi kisi zarurat ke tehat unke paas aaeyga, to wo kahengey, kal aana, Allah unhen raaton raat azab mein mubtala kar dega aur pahad un par gira dega jabkey baqi logon ki soorten maskh karkey roze-qiyamat tak bandar aur khinzir bana dega.'' Bukhari. aur masaabeh ke baaz nuskhon mein ''khaz'' ke bajaey ''hur'' hai aur ye tasheef hai, jabkey sahih ''khaz'' hai, Humedi aur ibne-aseer ne is hadees mein usi ko raajeh qarar diya hai, aur kitab Humedi mein Imam Bukhari ki sanad sey, aur isi tarah Bukhari ki sharah khattabi mein hai : ( تَرُوْحُ عَلَیْھِمْ سَارِحَۃٌ لَھُمْ یَأْتِیْھِمْ لِحَاجَۃِ ( Bukhari w fi masaabeh) ."
5344,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah kisi qom par azab nazil karta hai to tamam log us azab ki lapet mein aa jatey hain, phir wo apney apney aamaal ke mutabiq ( roze-qiyamat ( uthaey jaeyngey.'' muttafaq aleh."
5345,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her banda apney aakhiri amal par, jis par wo faut hua, uthaya jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim."
5346,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine jahannam ki misl koi chiz nahin dekhi ke jis se bhagney wala khuwab ghaflat mein ho, aur na hi jannat ki nematon w suroor ke misl koi chiz dekhi hai jis ka chaahney wala khuwab ghaflat mein ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5347,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo main dekh raha hun wo tum nahin dekhtey aur jo main sunta hun wo tum nahin suntey, aasman ne aawaz nikali aur usey char-charaney ki aawaz nikaalni bhi chahiye, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai! wahan her chaar angusht par farishta apni peshani rakhey huey Allah ke huzur sar b-sujood hai, Allah ki qasam! agar tum jaan lo jo main janta hun to tum kam hanso aur ziyada roo, tum bistaron par aurton (biwiyon) se lutf andoz hona chhod do aur tum sehraaon ki taraf nikal jaao aur Allah ke huzur (duaon ke zariey) aah w zaari karo.'' Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kash! main eik darkht hota jo kaat diya jata. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
5348,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs (raat ke aakhiri hissey mein safar karney sey) darta ho wo raat ke ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey mein safar ka aaghaz karta hai aur jo shakhs raat ke ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey mein safar karta hai to wo manzil par pahunch jata hai, sun lo! Allah ka saman qeemti hai, sun lo ! Allah ka saman jannat hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5349,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah, uska zikr azeemushshan ho, farmaeyga : her us shakhs ko jahannam ki aag se nikal do jisney (ikhlas ke sath) kisi eik roz bhi mujhey yad kya ho ya wo kisi jagah mujh se dara ho.'' (rawahu Tirmizi w al-Behaqi fi kitab al-ba's w nushoor) ."
5350,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us aayat : ''wo log detey hain, jo kuch detey hain, aur is par unke dil khaufzada hain.'' ke mutalliq daryaft kya, kya us se murad wo log hain jo sharab peetey aur chori kartey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''siddiq ki beti ! nahin, balke us se murad wo log hain jo rozey rakhtey hain, Namaz padhtey hain aur sadqa kartey hain, aur wo dartey hain ke kahin aisey na ho ke wo un se qubul na ho, yehi log nekiyon mein jaldi kartey hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
5351,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka mamool tha ke jab do tihai raat guzar jati to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho jatey aur farmatey : ''logo! Allah ka zikr karo, Allah ka zikr karo, zalzala aaney wala hai, uskey muttasil baad doosra zalzala aaney wala hai, aur maut apni sakhtiyon ke sath aa gaee aur maut apni sakhtiyon ke sath aa gaee.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5352,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz ke liye tashrif laye to aapney logon ko dekha goya wo hans rahey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo! agar tum lazzaton ko khatm kar deney wali) maut (ka kasrat se zikr kartey to wo tumhen us chiz ( hansney ( sey, jo maine dekhi hai, tumhen baaz rakhti, tum lazzaton ko khatm karney wali chiz yani maut ka kasrat se zikr karo, kyonkey qabr her roz kehti hai : main ghair manus ka ghar hun, main tanhai ka ghar hun, main mitti ka ghar hun aur main keedon makodon ka ghar hun, aur jab banda momin dafn kya jata hai to qabr usey khush aamadeed kehti hai, sun lo! meri satah par chalney waley afrad se to mujhey sab se ziyada pasand tha, aaj to merey supurd kar diya gaya hai, aur to merey paas aa gaya hai, to apney sath mera sulook dekhega.'' farmaya : '' wo uski had nazar tak uskey liye faraakh kar di jati hai aur uskey liye jannat ki taraf eik darwaza khol diya jata hai, aur jab faajir banda ya kafir shakhs dafn kya jata hai to qabr usey kehti hai : terey liye kisi qism ka khair maqadam nahin, sun ley! meri satah par chalney waley tamam afrad se to mujhey ziyada napasand tha, to aaj merey supurd kya gaya hai, aur to merey paas aa gaya hai, to an-qareeb apney sath mera sulook dekh lega.'' farmaya : ''wo is par tang ho jati hai, yahan tak ke uski pasliyan eik doosrey mein ghus jati hain.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye keyfiyat karkey dikhai ke aapney eik haath ki ungliyan doosrey haath ki ungliyon mein dakhil kin, aur farmaya : ''is par sattar azdahey musallat kar diye jaeyngey, aur agar un mein se eik zamin par phunk maar dey to wo ( zamin ( rehti duniya tak koi chiz na ugaey, wo usey dastey aur nochtey rahengey yahan tak ke usey hisab tak pahuncha diya jaeyga.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qabr to baaghon mein se eik baagh hai ya jahannam ke ghadon mein se eik gadha hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5353,"Hazrat abu Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Sahaba ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! aap boodhey ho gaey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Sura Hud aur us jaisi Suraton ne mujhey boodha kar diya.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5354,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! aap to boodhey ho gaey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Sura Hood, waqia, Mursalaat, Naba aur Sura shams ne mujhey boodha kar diya hai.'' Tirmizi, aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : '' jahannam mein dakhil nahin hoga.'' (baabul-Jihad) mein zikr ki gaee hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5355,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : tum aisey aamaal kartey ho jo tumhari nazron mein baal se bhi ziyada bareek hain (yani nihayat maamuli hain) jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehad mein ham unhen mohlik shumar kya kartey they. Bukhari."
5356,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aaisha! chhotey gunahon se bhi ijtinab karo kyonkey un gunahon ke liye bhi Allah ki taraf se (azab ka ( mutalba karney wala hai.'' (rawahu ibne-Maja w Darmi w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( .
5357,"Hazrat abu-Barda bin abu Musa bayan kartey hain, Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey farmaya : kya tum jantey ho ke merey walid ne aap ke walid se kya farmaya tha? unhoney kaha : mujhey ilm nahin, unhoney farmaya : merey walid ne aap ke walid se kaha : Abu-Musa kya ye baat tumhen khush karti hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein hamara Islam, aap ke sath mein hamari hijrat aur aap ke sath mein hamara jihad aur aap ke sath ham ne jo bhi amal kiye wo hamarey liye Sabit w barqarar rahen, aur ham ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad jo amal kiye hain, ham un mein barabar barabar (gunah na sawab) reh jaeyn? is par aap ke walid ne merey walid se kaha : nahin, Allah ki qasam! ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad jihad kya, namazein padhin, rozey rakhey, bahut se nek kaam kiye aur bahut se logon ne hamarey haathon par Islam qubul kya, aur ham un kamon ke sawab ki ummid rakhtey hain, merey walid ne kaha : lekin mein, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki jaan hai! ye pasand karta hun ke wo aamaal ( jo ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath kiye) hamarey liye Sabit rahen, aur wo tamam aamaal jo ham ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad kiye, un mein ham barabar barabar najat pa jaeyn, mein) abu-Barda ( ne kaha : be-shak aap ke walid (Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) , Allah ki qism ! merey walid se behtar they. Bukhari ."
5358,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey rab ne mujhey no chizon ka hukm farmaya : poshida w elaaniya her haalat mein Allah ka dar rakhna, ghazab w raza mein haq baat karna, faqr w maaldaari mein miyaana rawi ikhtiyar karna, jo shakhs mujh se qata talluq karey main uskey sath talluq qaaim karun, jo shakhs mujhey mehroom rakhey mein usey ata karun, jis shakhs ne mujh par zulm kya main usey maaf karun, mera khamosh rehna ghor w fikr ka pesh khema ho, mera bolnaa zikr ho aur mera dekhna ibrat ho, aur ye ke main neki ka hukm dun.'' rawahu rizeen ."
5359,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis momin bandey ki aakhon se Allah ke dar ke pesh nazar aansu nikal ayen, chahey wo makkhi ke sar ke barabar hun, phir wo uskey chehrey par aa jaeyn to Allah us shakhs ko jahannam ki aag par haram qarar dey deta hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
5360,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' log (apney halaat w sifaat ke ikhtilaf ke lihaz sey) un so oonton ki tarah hain jin main tum eik bhi sawari ke qabil na paao.'' muttafaq aleh."
5361,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum apney se pehley logon ke tariqon ki perwi w muwaafiqat karogey jis tarah baalisht baalisht ke barabar aur haath haath ke barabar hota hai, yahan tak ke agar wo saandey ke bil mein ghusey hongey to tum bhi unki muwaafiqat karogey.'' arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool! (pehley logon se murad) yahood w nasaara? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''to phir aur kon hain ?'' muttafaq aleh."
5362,"Hazrat Mirdas Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nek log eik eik karkey chaley jaeyngey, aur be kaar log baqi reh jaeyngey jaisey jo ka bhoosa ya khajoor ka kachra baqi reh jata hai jinki Allah ke yahan koi qadr w qeemat nahin hogi.'' Bukhari ."
5363,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab meri ummat takabburana chaal chalegi aur baadshaahon ke bete (yani) Faaris w Rome ke shahzaadey unke khaadim bin jaeyngey to Allah is ( ummat (ke burey logon ko unke achey logon par musallat farma dega.'' Tirmizi aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
5364,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi jab tak tum apney khalifa ko qatl nahin karogey, baham (aapas mein) qatl w gharat nahin karogey aur tumharey burey log tumhari duniya ke waris nahin bin jaeyngey.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5365,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke zaleel w kamina shakhs duniya (ke maal w mataa aur ohda w mansab) se sab se ziyada behramand hoga.'' ( rawahu Tirmizi w al-Behaqi fi dalaylunnubuwa) ."
5366,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Kab Qarzi bayan kartey hain, mujhey us shakhs ne hadees bayan ki jisney Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se suna : unhoney farmaya : ham masjid mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath bethey huey they ke achcha Musab bin Umer (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas aaye un par sirf eik hi chadar thi jis par chamdey ke pewand lagey huey they, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen dekha to aap unki sabiqa nematon wali haalat aur aaj ki haalat ka farq dekh kar roney lagey, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhari haalat kya hogi jab tum mein se koi shakhs din ke pehley pahar eik joda pehneyga aur din ke doosrey pahar doosra joda pehnega, unke dasterkhaan par eik tashtri rakhi jaeygi aur dusri uthai jaeygi, aur tum apney gharon ko (pardon aur sajawat ki chizon sey) is tarah dhaanpogey jis tarah Kaba ko (ghilafon ke sath) dhanpa jata hai.'' Sahaba ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! us waqt ham aaj ki nisbat behtar hongey, ham ibadat ke liye farigh hongey aur ham kaam kaaj se farigh kar diye jaeyngey (mulaazim kaam karengey) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin, us waqt ki nisbat aaj tum behtar ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5367,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon par eik aisa waqt bhi aaeyga ke us waqt apney Deen par qaaim rehney wala angaara pakadney waley ki tarah hoga.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : is hadees ki sanad gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
5368,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumharey umra wo hongey jo tum mein sab se behtar hongey, tumharey maal daar log sakhi aur tumharey maamlat aapsi mashwarey se tey hongey to phir tumharey liye zamin ki pusht uskey pet se behtar hogi (yani zindagi maut se behtar hogi (aur jab tumharey hukmran burey log hongey, tumharey maal daar log bakheel aur tumharey maamlat aurton ke supurd hongey to phir tumharey liye zamin ka pet uski pusht se behtar hoga.'' ( maut zindagi se behtar hogi ( Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
5369,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qarib hai ke) gumrah ( qomen tumharey khilaf ( ladney ke liye) dusri qomon ko bulaeyn jis tarah khaney waley khaney ke bartan ki taraf eik doosrey ko bulatey hain.'' kisi ne arz kya is roz hamari tadaad kam honey ki wajeh se aisey hoga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, balke us roz tum ziyada hogey, lekin tum sailab ki jhaag ki tarah hogey , Allah tumharey dushmanon ke dilon se tumhari heybiyat nikal dega aur tumharey dil mein wahan dal dega.'' kisi ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! wahan kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' duniya se mohabbat aur maut se nafrat.'' (rawahu Abu-Dawood w al-Behaqi fi dalaeyl النبوۃ ( ."
5370,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jis qom mein khayanat aam ho jaey to Allah unke dilon mein roab dal deta hai, jis qom mein zina phel jaey to un mein mautein badh jati hain, jo qom naap tol mein kami karti hai to un se rizq rok liya jata hai, jo qom nahaq faisley karney lagey to un mein qatl aam ho jata hai aur jo qom ehad shikni karti hai to un par dushman musallat kar diya jata hai.'' rawahu malik."
5371,"Hazrat Ayaaz bin Himaar Majaashi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney khutbe mein irshad farmaya : ''sun lo ! merey rab ne mujhey hukm diya hai ke main tumhen us sey, jo usney mujhey aaj taalim di hai, wo chizen sikhaaun jo tum nahin jantey , wo tamam maal jo maine kisi bandey ko ata kya hai wo halal hai, maine apney tamam bandon ko hunafaa (batil se door rehney waley aur haq qubul karney ke liye tayyar rehney waley) paida kiya hai, be-shak shayatin unke paas aatey hain aur wo unhen unke Deen se door kar detey hain, aur maine unke liye jo halal kiya tha wo un chizon ko un par haram kar detey hain, aur wo unhen hukm detey hain ke wo merey sath shareek karen jiski maine koi daleel nahin utaari , be-shak Allah ne ehale-zameen ki taraf dekha to usney ehle-kitab ke kuchh logon ke siwa unke Arab aur ajam ko mabghuz thehra diya, aur farmaya : maine aap ko sirf isliye mab-us (bheja) kiya hai ta ke main aap ko aazmaun aur aap ke zariey (aap ki qom ko) aazmaun, maine aap par kitab utaari jisey pani nahin dho sakta (naqaabile-tanseekh hai), aap isey sotey jaagtey padhengey , be-shak Allah ne mujhey Quraish ko halak karney ka hukm farmaya to maine arz kiya : merey parwardigar ! wo mera sar kuchal dengey aur usey roti bana dengey, farmaya : aap unhen nikal den jaisey unhoney aap ko nikal diya tha aap un se jihad karen, ham aap ko tayyar karengey , aap kharch karen, aap par kharch kiya jaeyga, aap lashkar bhejein , ham bhi uske jaise (farishton ke) paanch lashkar bhejeingey , aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney itaat guzaaron ke sath nafarmanon ke khilaf qitaal keren.'' rawahu Muslim."
5372,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ye aayat : ''apney qaribi rishtey daaron ko daraeyn.'' nazil hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Safa pahadi par chadh kar aawaz deney lagey : bano fahar ! bano Adi ! (jo ke Quraish ke qabiley hain) yahan tak ke wo ikhattey ho gaey, to farmaya : ''mujhey bataao agar main tumhen khabar dun ke wadi main eik lashkar hai jo tum par hamla karna chahta hai to kya tum meri tasdeeq karogey?'' unhoney kaha : ji , ham ne aap ko sachcha hi paya hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main azabe-shadeed se pehley tumhen aagah karney wala hun.'' Abu-Lahab ne kaha : baqi din mein terey liye halakat ho, kya tum ne isliye hamein jama kiya tha, tab surat  (تَبَّتْ يَدَآ اَبِيْ لَهَبٍ وَّتَبَّ) ''Abu Lahab ke haath toot jaeyn aur wo tabah aur barbad ho jaey.'' nazil hui . eik dusri riwayat mein hai, aapney aawaz di '' bano abd munaaf ! meri aur tumhari misal us shakhs ki tarah hai jisney dushman ko dekha to wo apney ehal aur ayaal ko bachaney chala to usey andesha hua ke wo (dushman) is par sabqat ley jaeyngey to wo (dushman ki ittilaa deney ke liye) zor zor se kehta hai : ya sabaa haa.'' muttafaq aleh."
5373,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ye aayat : '' apney qaribi rishtey daaron ko daraoo.'' nazil hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Quraish ko aawaz di, wo sab jama ho gaey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aam aur khas sabhi ko mukhatib kartey huey farmaya : aey bani Kab bin Luee ! apney aap ko jahannam ki aag se azad kara lo , aey bano Murra bin Kab ! apney aap ko aag se bachaaw , aey bano Abd Shams ! apney aap ko aag se bachaaw , bano Abdul Muttalib ! apney aap ko aag se bachaaw , Fatima ! apney aap ko aag se bachaaw. mein Allah ke yahan tumharey liye kisi chiz ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta , albatta jo haq qurbat hai main usey ehsan ke sath nibhaaoonga.'' aur Sahih Bukhari aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Quraish ki jamaat ! apni jaanon ko (emaan ke sath aag sey) bachaaw, mein Allah ke yahan tumharey kuchh kaam nahin aaunga , bano Abd Munaaf ! main Allah ke yahan tumharey kuchh kaam nahin aaunga , Abbas bin Abdul Muttalib ! main Allah ke yahan tumharey kuchh kaam nahin aaunga, Rasulullah ki phuphi Safiya ! main Allah ke yahan tumharey kuchh kaam nahin aaunga, Fatima binte Muhammad ! merey maal mein se jo chaho ley lo, main Allah ke yahan tumharey kuchh kaam nahin aaunga.'' rawahu Muslim aur Bukhari."
5374,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ye ummat , ummat marhooma (jis par rehem kiya gaya) hai, is par aakhirat mein (shadeed) azab nahin, duniya mein iska azab fitnon , zalzalon aur qatl ki surat mein hoga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5375,"Hazrat Abu Ubeda aur Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is Deen ka aaghaz nabuwat aur rehmat se hua , phir khilaafat aur rehmat hogi , phir zalim badshah hongey, phir zamin mein jabr , ziyadti aur fasad hoga, wo resham , sharam gaahon (zina) aur sharab ko halal samjhengey, unhen usi haalat par rizq diya jaeyga aur unki madad ki jati rahegi yahan tak ke wo Allah se ja milengey.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5376,"Hazrat Abu Ubeda aur Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is Deen ka aaghaz nabuwat aur rehmat se hua , phir khilaafat aur rehmat hogi , phir zalim badshah hongey, phir zamin mein jabr , ziyadti aur fasad hoga, wo resham , sharam gaahon (zina) aur sharab ko halal samjhengey , unhen usi haalat par rizq diya jaeyga aur unki madad ki jati rahegi yahan tak ke wo Allah se ja milengey.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5377,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''be-shak sab se pehley ulta diya jaeyga, Zaid bin Yahya raawi ne bayan kiya, yani Islam , jaisey bartan ulta diya jata hai, yani sharab , arz kiya gaya : Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ne iskey mutalliq to wazahat farma di hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : wo iska naam badal lengey aur phir isey halal janengey.'' rawahu Darmi."
5378,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir , Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak Allah chaheyga tum mein nabuwat (ke asraat) baqi rakhega , phir Allah Taala usey utha lega, phir jab tak Allah chaheyga , khilaafat nabuwat ke andaz par hogi, phir Allah Taala usey bhi utha lega, phir jis qadr Allah chaheyga kaatney waley badshah hongey phir Allah Taala usey bhi utha lega , phir jabriya badshahat hogi aur ye bhi jab tak Allah chaheyga rahegi, phir Allah Taala isey bhi utha lega , phir khilaafat nabuwat ki tarz par hogi.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh ho gaey. Habib bayan kartey hain, jab umr bin Abdul Azeez (Reh.) ne khilaafat sanbhaali to maine unki yad dahani ke liye unhen ye hadees likhi , aur kaha : main ummid karta hun ke zalim badshah aur jabriya badshahat ke baad aap Ameerul Momineen hain. wo is se khush huey aur unhen achchhaa laga. (rawahu Ahmed aur al-Behaqi)."
